snippet.title: Dirt 5 - Official Wild Spirits Content Pack Trailer
snippet.description:
Dirt 5's Wild Spirits content pack brings the Ford Bronco 2021 Wildtrak, as well as the Prodrive Hunter, along with another 25 Career events, two new Player Sponsors, customization items, and more. Check out the trailer for a look at what to expect.

The Wild Spirits content pack for Dirt 5 is available now for Xbox One, Xbox Series X/S, PlayStation 5, PlayStation 4, and PC.

#GameTrailers #Gaming #Dirt5
